{"tid":1531842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為公義 為良知 10/9 係香港人嘅唔該一齊入場撐香港","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T08:59:40.000Z","uid":51596,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"c48ce4df99b3e0deb27f2266c5f6d6f49891c62b","tid":1531842,"uid":51596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:51:41.000Z","msg":"一切源於呢個post:<br />\n<blockquote>香港球迷幾時着波衫一齊搞個集會？如果利物浦曼聯車路士球迷都企埋一齊嘅話應該幾吸睛....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n足球與政治從來都分唔開，香港好多球迷會已經出哂聲！今次<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到我地球迷表態 支持球迷會 支持香港人</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n我哋係香港人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人最重要係撐我哋香港隊！</span></span>10/9 大球場香港對伊朗場波一齊入場，一齊叫口號，俾各位朋友知道香港發生乜事！<br />\n<br />\n當日嘅dresscode係：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">波衫！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不論你有自己愛隊定或港隊波衫，唔該當日着入場！當然如果自己愛隊同港隊都有嘅...一齊帶入去！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n開波時間：10/9 20:00<br />\n地點：香港大球場<br />\n票價：成人$180 長者/學生：$40<br />\n買飛link：<a href=\"https://venue.cityline.com/utsvInternet/enrollment/action/event.do?actionFwd=eventDetail&amp;event=31912&amp;activityCode=EAFF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvenue.cityline.com%2FutsvInternet%2Fenrollment%2Faction%2Fevent.do%3FactionFwd%3DeventDetail%26event%3D31912%26activityCode%3DEAFF&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR24L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=bc1dec87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://venue.cityline.com/utsvInternet/enrollment/action/event.do?actionFwd=eventDetail&amp;event=31912&amp;activityCode=EAFF</a> （更加可以選擇當日即場買飛！）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有球迷 不分你我<br />\n自己香港自己救<br />\n自己球隊自己撐<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n香港人撐香港波 一齊入場支持屬於大家嘅球隊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再有新消息，都喺呢個TG Group發怖： <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AbirsRWg4mBGV10CZdp-FQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAbirsRWg4mBGV10CZdp-FQ&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR24L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=a8d8d2e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AbirsRWg4mBGV10CZdp-FQ</a>"},{"pid":"427f6fabe0c5630e5367c244fc36a47c4b7d9bf2","tid":1531842,"uid":241543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:52:22.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7b91b02b646e16ba2be0dec99245be2df92f6fd2","tid":1531842,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"90042e52d03df0721d4b82751728fc90edcda81e","tid":1531842,"uid":4750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"233c73f7bef811eb55461695321475ef85f21eaf","tid":1531842,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"推爆佢！"},{"pid":"5fb0169aba56171fa99336c2cae8020362aff57f","tid":1531842,"uid":154738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7a58b4f66b6222ab23524f9c5671f3a62c91572","tid":1531842,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"泥妹路過幫推"},{"pid":"0241accd1d0ac8d1ae85763b2188d53ef77c26a4","tid":1531842,"uid":198455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ce5f60b09ed0eed931f9b7a8dbb086811c2f9e","tid":1531842,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"86f1e87523ae749d09ea6b94512336f8306a8370","tid":1531842,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":